      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i had a small cyst removed by a doctor like 3 days ago here in sydney and the cut looks a bit weird. its kind of red and feels warm and there is some yellow stuff oozing out but it doesnt really hurt that much. can i just put some antibiotic cream on it and a warm cloth to stop it? i dont really wanna go back to the clinic unless i have to",
